long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing Wilfie AI Chat powered by Chat GPT 4, the ultimate Chrome extension. With Wilfie AI Chat, you can easily chat with your personal AI assistant, Wilfie, while using any website in your browser. 

Gone are the days of switching between websites and apps just to get things done. Whether you need help with responding to an email, researching, summarising a page or translations, Wilfie is here to assist you. 

Wilfie AI Chat is always just a click away, conveniently located in your Chrome browser. Simply install the extension and start chatting with your new virtual assistant today. Say goodbye to wasted time and frustration and hello to a more efficient browsing experience with Wilfie AI Chat.

All your chat history is available at https://wilfie.ai.
